   "source": [
    "### EX1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "93fdc59c-d788-4061-8e0e-e33593922ba9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "`-` 현실에서 이런경우가 많음: \n",
    "- $x$가 커질수록 (작아질수록) 성공확률이 증가 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a00c4f69-11c0-44d9-bcb3-de60d4252159",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "`-` 이러한 모형은 아래와 같이 설계할 수 있음 (왜?) <--- 외우세요.. !!! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a1503dfd-3718-478d-9669-e5b9db83d876",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- $y_i \\sim Ber(p_i),\\quad $ where $p_i=\\frac{\\exp(\\beta_0+\\beta_1x_i)}{1+\\exp(\\beta_0+\\beta_1x_i)}$\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e3167329-20d1-481e-b015-3a32c952d558",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- $\\hat{y}_i= \\frac{\\exp(\\hat{\\beta}_0+\\hat{\\beta}_1 x_i)}{1+\\exp(\\hat{\\beta}_0+\\hat{\\beta}_1x_i)}=\\frac{1}{1+\\exp(-\\hat{\\beta}_0-\\hat{\\beta}_1x_i)}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e05a31e7-9b13-4b1f-86a1-90e0e3183af3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- $loss=  -\\sum_{i=1}^{n}\\big(y_i\\log(\\hat{y}_i)+(1-y_i)\\log(1-\\hat{y}_i) \\big)$ <--- 외우세요!!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "6faf80f7-cf45-4df7-83cd-801e1483e31c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "torch.manual_seed(1)\n",
    "X=torch.linspace(-1,1,2000).reshape(2000,1)\n",
    "w0= -1\n",
    "w1= 5\n",
    "u=X*w1+w0\n",
    "v=torch.exp(u)/(1+(torch.exp(u)))\n",
    "y=torch.bernoulli(v)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "884728cb-a54f-4548-9c28-0d609fc6823c",
   "metadata": {},
